name: Title Jungle
description: Title sequence with Sven bursting out of the jungle to the title sequence.

name: Satellite Repair
description: Sven repairs satellite talking to Kiera.

name: Space Fall
description: Sven breaks through the atmosphere and his ship is damaged by the Trilobot.

name: Satellite Attack
description: Sven is attacked by the Trilobot and makes it to his ship.

name: Fall Surface
description: Sven breaks free from his chair and surfaces.

name: Fall Water
description: Sven ejects and his ship crashes into the water.

name: Beach Communicate
description: Sven calls Kiera and finds out the Killamari are on the planet.

name: Beach Attack
description: The Trilobot finds Sven and blasts at his position behind a rock.

name: Beach Survey
description: Sven surveys the coast and finds a beach that he swims to.

name: Jungle Run
description: Sven runs through Jungle chased by the Trilobot

name: Jungle Fruit
description: Sven sees a fruit explode and gets an idea.

name: Jungle Lava
description: Sven downs a tree and destroys the Trilobot.

name: Jungle Plateau
description: Sven exits the jungle into the Plateau

name: Plateau
description: Sven approaches the edge and sees the Killamari City
